Package <Unnamed>

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    HtmlComponent
    An interface that can be drawn by a HtmlCanvas.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HtmlCanvas
    Performs the actual rendering of HtmlComponents.
    HtmlFragment
    A single element of HTML to be rendered by a HtmlCanvas, containing String, Font and a Color.
    HtmlPrinter
    A client that manages printing to a HtmlCanvas.
    HtmlTag
    A HtmlComponent for HTML-style tags that cannot be expressed easily as text, such as the <br> and {@code
    SimpleHtmlRenderer
    The main class for SimpleHtmlRenderer, a program that can help pretty-print tokenized HTML.
